    <item>
      <title>美国敦促中国在知识产权保护方面更加透明</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/us-presses-china-to-be-more-transparent-on-ip-protection</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国商务官员凯西·维达尔 (Kathi Vidal) 表示，随着美国大选年贸易紧张局势迫在眉睫，北京需要更清楚地了解如何保护知识产权并解决新形式的侵权行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/us-presses-china-to-be-more-transparent-on-ip-protection</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 02:55:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东问题、鹰派美联储情绪低迷，亚洲股市暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/asian-stocks-slump-as-mideast-woes-hawkish-fed-sour-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中东紧张局势升级的担忧以及对美国利率长期走高的担忧，市场普遍出现避险情绪，亚洲股市暴跌。]]></description>
